    <title type="html"><![CDATA[xUtils在开发过程中DbUtils的使用]]></title>
    <link href="http://xupingwei.github.io/blog/2015/12/13/02/"/>
    <updated>2015-12-13T17:18:56+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://xupingwei.github.io/blog/2015/12/13/02</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>xUtils在开发过程中DbUtils的使用</h1>

<h3>1.DbUtils中的save的用法</h3>

<h5>1）根据官网save的方法很好用</h5>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>代码 <a href="http://xupingwei.github.io/">http://xupingwei.github.io/</a> 链接 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='java'><span class='line'>    <span class="n">dbUtils</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">save</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">userDetails</span><span class="o">);</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
- userDetails：实体类的对象&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;直接调用save方法进行保存，很容易不再啰嗦</p>

<h3>2.DbUtils中的update的用法</h3>

<h5>1）update用法</h5>

<ul>
<li>在调用dbUtils.update(&hellip;)时，有时会出现NOT FOUND &ldquo;id"的错误&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-这是因为在执行update方法时，传入的参数出现错误</li>
<li><p>正确的用法是：
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>代码  <a href="http://xupingwei.github.io/">http://xupingwei.github.io/</a> 链接 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='java'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="n">code</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>  <span class="n">dbUtils</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">update</span><span class="o">(</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="n">userDetails</span><span class="o">,</span><span class="n">WhereBuilder</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">b</span><span class="o">(</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="s">&quot;phone&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">&quot;=&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">userDetails</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">getPhone</span><span class="o">()),</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="s">&quot;avatarname&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span><span class="s">&quot;username&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span><span class="s">&quot;gender&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">&quot;birthday&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="s">&quot;business&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">&quot;grade&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">&quot;city&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">&quot;area&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">&quot;address&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="s">&quot;progress&quot;</span><span class="o">);</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">code</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="n">li</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">ul</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<ul>
<li>userDetails:需要跟新的实体类对象</li>
<li>&ldquo;phone"：根据表中的列名称进行跟新</li>
<li>userDetails.getPhone():称更新实体类对象的唯一值</li>
<li>&ldquo;avatarname"，"username"：需要更新的列名称</li>
</ul>


<h3>3.DbUtils中的find的用法：</h3>

<h5>1) findFirst用法</h5>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>代码  <a href="http://xupingwei.github.io/">http://xupingwei.github.io/</a> 链接 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='java'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="n">code</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="n">lastTime</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">dbUtils</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">findFirst</span><span class="o">(</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">Selector</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">from</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">UserDetails</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">class</span><span class="o">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>        <span class="o">.</span><span class="na">where</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">WhereBuilder</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">b</span><span class="o">(</span>
</span><span class='line'>            <span class="s">&quot;lastmodifytime&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="s">&quot;=&quot;</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="n">time</span><span class="o">)));</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">code</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<ul>
<li>Selector.from(UserDetails.class)：查找哪张表（这里查找的是UserDetails这张表）</li>
<li>WhereBuilder.b(&ldquo;lastmodifytime&rdquo;, &ldquo;=&rdquo;, time)：条件查询</li>
</ul>


<h5>2）findAll用法</h5>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>代码 <a href="http://xupingwei.github.io/">http://xupingwei.github.io/</a> 链接 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='java'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="n">code</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="n">mList</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">dbUtils</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">findAll</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">UserDetails</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">class</span><span class="o">);</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">code</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<h5>3) findDbModelFirst</h5>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span>代码 <a href="http://xupingwei.github.io/">http://xupingwei.github.io/</a> 链接 </span></figcaption>
<div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='java'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="n">code</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="n">dbUtils</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">findDbModelFirst</span><span class="o">(</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="n">Selector</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">from</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">Category</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">class</span><span class="o">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>            <span class="o">.</span><span class="na">select</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="k">new</span> <span class="n">String</span><span class="o">[]{</span><span class="s">&quot;lastupdate&quot;</span><span class="o">}));</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;/</span><span class="n">code</span><span class="o">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="n">pre</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<ul>
<li>DbModel&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-相当于表的一个视图，把其当做视图看待</li>
<li>select(new String[]{&ldquo;lastupdate&rdquo;})&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-这个视图中包含的属性，这里包含的属性是“lastupdate”</li>
<li>如果需要包含其他的属性，直接在new String[]{}里增加表的字段</li>
</ul>

]]></content>
